tspan.tspan: Hatch Architects Design Center is a nonprofit created in 2021. Our mission is to enhance the community by
empowering students with design skills and knowledge while simultaneously improving our built environment. We
are primarily focused on the City of Dayton and Dayton Public School students.
Our nonprofit aims to increase the diversity in the architecture profession and inspire young people to explore the
profession and pursue it themselves! Through hands-on workshops with guest architect and designers as mentors,
we hope to hatch more community-minded architects.
